# Django PostreSQL Nginx Gunicorn

## Set up Docker

1. Create `Dockerfile`
2. Create `docker-compose.yml` file
3. Create `requirements.txt` file
4. Create an image by executing `docker compose build`
5. Create container by executing `docker compose run --rm app django-admin startproject core .`
6. Start container by executing `docker compose up`
7. Create terminal for container by executing `docker exec -it django_app /bin/bash`
8. Access database on container by executing `docker exec -ti postgres_db psql -U postgres`